Twenty-seven years ago, their targets were all young women.

288
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:44,850
But Liang Chuyi and Qiuhua,

289
00:16:45,240 --> 00:16:46,770
they were both older women.

290
00:16:47,280 --> 00:16:48,480
Why is that?

291
00:16:48,920 --> 00:16:50,450
There's a new development.

292
00:16:50,840 --> 00:16:51,640
Constable Su.

293
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:52,840
Any clues?

294
00:16:53,760 --> 00:16:55,020
You two guessed right.

295
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:56,480
Old Liang's little grandson in the country

296
00:16:56,480 --> 00:16:57,480
has gone missing.

297
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:59,040
When did he go missing?

298
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:01,720
He disappeared the day after he went back to the country.

299
00:17:01,720 --> 00:17:03,120
I remember Old Liang said

300
00:17:03,240 --> 00:17:05,119
his little grandson has asthma.

301
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:08,200
With this disease, he needs to have medicine on him at all times.

302
00:17:08,200 --> 00:17:08,920
Wrong.

303
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,119
Wrong.

304
00:17:11,119 --> 00:17:11,720
Wrong.

305
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:13,400
I was just at Honglian's.

306
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:14,400
She told me

307
00:17:14,720 --> 00:17:16,760
Qiuhua had severe kidney consumption.

308
00:17:16,760 --> 00:17:18,520
Her lover wasn't some wealthy merchant.

309
00:17:18,520 --> 00:17:19,599
It was Wang Mang.

310
00:17:20,040 --> 00:17:21,300
It all makes sense now.

311
00:17:21,599 --> 00:17:24,720
Someone deliberately kidnapped Old Liang's grandson.

312
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:27,380
We must search all the pharmacies immediately.

313
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:29,660
Whoever buys asthma medicine regularly

314
00:17:30,400 --> 00:17:32,160
is the biggest suspect.

315
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:33,600
Go.

316
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:43,610
Go upstairs.

317
00:17:44,280 --> 00:17:44,720
Go.

318
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:01,160
Dad, careful.

319
00:18:04,440 --> 00:18:06,680
I searched all the pharmacies nearby.

320
00:18:10,800 --> 00:18:12,660
The owner of this pharmacy told me

321
00:18:13,120 --> 00:18:16,520
someone recently bought a large amount of Shegan Mahuang Decoction

322
00:18:16,520 --> 00:18:18,120
and Dingchuan Decoction.

323
00:18:21,520 --> 00:18:22,520
And this person,

324
00:18:23,120 --> 00:18:25,120
his right shoulder is lower than his left.

325
00:18:25,120 --> 00:18:25,520
Are you okay?

326
00:18:25,520 --> 00:18:27,240
He looks like a porter.

327
00:18:28,960 --> 00:18:30,360
And coincidentally,

328
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,880
this pharmacy

329
00:18:32,760 --> 00:18:34,480
is very close to

330
00:18:34,800 --> 00:18:36,080
Qiuhua's house.

331
00:18:38,880 --> 00:18:40,340
I've had asthma these days

332
00:18:40,520 --> 00:18:41,580
and need medicine.

333
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:46,160
Uncle Liang's grandson is unconscious upstairs.

334
00:18:46,160 --> 00:18:47,720
Save the child quickly.

335
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:48,960
He's fine.

336
00:18:50,080 --> 00:18:52,540
I gave him a soothing soup and he fell asleep.

337
00:18:57,280 --> 00:18:58,800
How did you find me?

338
00:18:59,520 --> 00:19:00,720
Uncle Liang told you?

339
00:19:01,320 --> 00:19:03,400
Uncle Liang did as you said.

340
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:07,360
Indeed, he committed all the murders 27 years ago.

341
00:19:07,560 --> 00:19:09,880
But Qiuhua and Liang Chuyi now,

342
00:19:10,000 --> 00:19:11,520
they were killed by you.

343
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,840
In all the previous murders,

344
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:16,560
the suspect would carefully dress up each victim.

345
00:19:16,560 --> 00:19:17,680
This detail

346
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:19,460
is generally not noticed.

347
00:19:22,960 --> 00:19:24,520
I also used this point

348
00:19:25,360 --> 00:19:27,720
to confirm he is the killer of my sister.

349
00:19:29,840 --> 00:19:31,570
Every day since my sister died,

350
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,720
I've blamed myself

351
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:35,160
and hated myself.

352
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:36,960
From that day on,

353
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,880
I only have one reason to live,

354
00:19:38,920 --> 00:19:40,720
and that is to avenge my sister.

355
00:19:52,280 --> 00:19:52,880
Later,

356
00:19:53,800 --> 00:19:56,260
I went to Constable Qin to ask about the case.

357
00:19:56,920 --> 00:19:58,580
Since the case was not solved,

358
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,120
out of guilt,

359
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:02,760
he told me all the details.

360
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:07,260
The masked man's route was from the pier to the East Market.

361
00:20:07,760 --> 00:20:10,290
He suspected the masked man lived at the pier.

362
00:20:10,680 --> 00:20:13,280
So I've been a porter at the pier since I grew up,

363
00:20:13,840 --> 00:20:15,760
wanting to meet more people

364
00:20:16,640 --> 00:20:18,480
and praying to meet him again.

365
00:20:20,200 --> 00:20:21,640
By chance,

366
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:25,000
I found a wooden stick on Uncle Liang's boat.

367
00:20:26,080 --> 00:20:27,600
I asked him what it was for.

368
00:20:28,520 --> 00:20:31,320
Uncle Liang told me it was for self-defense

369
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:34,680
and driving away water snakes.

370
00:20:40,000 --> 00:20:41,000
But that stick

371
00:20:41,040 --> 00:20:43,440
was very similar to the one I saw that night.

372
00:20:44,680 --> 00:20:47,760
Considering Uncle Liang's age matched the killer's,

373
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:50,890
I started paying attention to him.

374
00:20:52,480 --> 00:20:53,360
I observed that

375
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:55,320
whenever it rained,

376
00:20:56,120 --> 00:20:58,400
Uncle Liang would go home early.

377
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:03,060
I checked the boat departures on the day my sister died.

378
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:06,260
Although it didn't rain that day,

379
00:21:06,520 --> 00:21:08,240
the government opened navigation

380
00:21:08,240 --> 00:21:09,400
and sealed the port.

381
00:21:10,080 --> 00:21:12,200
None of the boatmen went out.

382
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:15,640
The only thing that didn't match

383
00:21:15,640 --> 00:21:17,770
was that Uncle Liang is right-handed,

384
00:21:17,800 --> 00:21:20,730
while the suspect injured people with his left hand.

385
00:21:21,680 --> 00:21:23,440
So I started testing him.

386
00:21:24,600 --> 00:21:27,600
Once I deliberately fell into the water from his boat.

387
00:21:28,160 --> 00:21:29,760
In the most critical moment,

388
00:21:32,360 --> 00:21:34,200
he reached out his left hand.

389
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:36,760
Afterwards,

390
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:39,280
I told Qiuhua the whole thing.

391
00:21:40,720 --> 00:21:42,080
But Qiuhua told me

392
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:45,040
The government won't accept an old case

393
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:47,170
without evidence after so many years,

394
00:21:47,320 --> 00:21:49,520
based solely on personal guesses.

395
00:22:06,240 --> 00:22:07,040
Brother Mang.

396
00:22:07,600 --> 00:22:08,800
Before I got sick,

397
00:22:09,800 --> 00:22:11,200
you said you'd marry me.

398
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:13,760
Is it true?

399
00:22:15,400 --> 00:22:16,640
Of course it's true.

400
00:22:27,840 --> 00:22:30,440
Do you want to bring the real killer to justice?

401
00:22:33,760 --> 00:22:34,760
I dream of it.

402
00:22:35,840 --> 00:22:37,000
I have a way.

403
00:22:39,360 --> 00:22:40,360
What way?

404
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:45,160
You,

405
00:22:45,920 --> 00:22:46,920
kill me.

406
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,240
Nonsense.

407
00:22:53,840 --> 00:22:55,160
I'm telling the truth.

408
00:22:56,000 --> 00:22:57,600
I won't live long anyway.

409
00:23:00,120 --> 00:23:01,680
Strangle me with a rope.

410
00:23:02,240 --> 00:23:05,700
Imitate the exact modus operandi of the killer from back then.

411
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,440
Then watch Uncle Liang's reaction.

412
00:23:07,440 --> 00:23:08,880
If he is the real killer,

413
00:23:09,840 --> 00:23:11,400
when everyone is talking about

414
00:23:11,400 --> 00:23:13,640
how the killer from back then is striking again,

415
00:23:13,640 --> 00:23:15,000
you try to get information out of him.

416
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:17,160
His reaction will definitely be different from others.

417
00:23:17,160 --> 00:23:18,640
Then you can report him to the officials.

418
00:23:18,640 --> 00:23:19,840
Say he

419
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:21,920
killed me.

420
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:24,600
No.

421
00:23:25,000 --> 00:23:25,680
No.

422
00:23:25,920 --> 00:23:26,840
I can't kill you.

423
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:27,520
No.

424
00:23:39,680 --> 00:23:41,000
Is there a difference

425
00:23:42,520 --> 00:23:44,050
between living one more day

426
00:23:45,480 --> 00:23:47,160
and ten more days?

427
00:23:51,000 --> 00:23:53,260
If the real killer doesn't strike again,

428
00:23:53,960 --> 00:23:55,880
you'll never catch him.

429
00:23:58,960 --> 00:24:01,400
But I want to help you catch him.

430
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,840
This is the last thing

431
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:11,480
I can do for you in my life.

432
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,840
I'm dying anyway.

433
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:36,120
I want my death

434
00:24:38,640 --> 00:24:40,480
to be more meaningful.

435
00:24:47,760 --> 00:24:48,800
I hope

436
00:24:50,520 --> 00:24:52,920
you can help me take good care of Zhen'er.

437
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:55,280
Can you?

438
00:25:01,040 --> 00:25:02,240
Can you?

439
00:25:16,160 --> 00:25:18,040
If you don't agree,

440
00:25:19,640 --> 00:25:21,560
I'll die right in front of you.

441
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:26,720
If you just stab him to death,

442
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:28,640
he'll never repent.

443
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:34,600
Bringing him to justice

444
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:39,760
is the real punishment.

445
00:25:42,560 --> 00:25:43,840
I can't kill you.

446
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,880
I can't kill you.

447
00:25:53,640 --> 00:25:54,720
I heard that

448
00:25:56,720 --> 00:25:58,000
before a person dies,

449
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:01,320
hearing is the last sense to go.

450
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:03,480
So,

451
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:07,240
please say you love me

452
00:26:08,920 --> 00:26:11,160
in my last moments.

453
00:26:22,320 --> 00:26:23,560
I love you.

454
00:26:27,720 --> 00:26:28,760
I love you.

455
00:26:55,600 --> 00:26:56,240
Zhen'er.

456
00:27:04,720 --> 00:27:06,650
When everyone started discussing

457
00:27:06,880 --> 00:27:09,610
whether the suspect from back then struck again,

458
00:27:10,480 --> 00:27:11,880
only Uncle Liang said no.

459
00:27:13,160 --> 00:27:14,890
Because in the previous cases,

460
00:27:15,400 --> 00:27:17,360
the victims' hair was tidy.

461
00:27:18,520 --> 00:27:19,800
But Qiuhua's wasn't.

462
00:27:20,520 --> 00:27:22,000
Her hair was messy.

463
00:27:23,280 --> 00:27:25,940
You were extremely shocked when you heard that.

464
00:27:28,200 --> 00:27:30,060
You didn't want to just let him go.

465
00:27:31,160 --> 00:27:31,840
So

466
00:27:32,640 --> 00:27:34,800
you thought of a crueler method.

467
00:27:35,600 --> 00:27:38,120
You made a mask like the one the killer wore

468
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,730
when he killed your sister.

469
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:42,890
You killed Uncle Liang's youngest daughter.

470
00:27:43,040 --> 00:27:44,520
You killed Liang Chuyi.

471
00:27:45,440 --> 00:27:47,440
They kidnapped his little grandson

472
00:27:47,760 --> 00:27:50,080
and threatened him with the boy's life,

473
00:27:51,680 --> 00:27:55,340
making Uncle Liang take the blame for murdering his own daughter.

474
00:27:55,880 --> 00:27:57,080
Suxiang,

475
00:27:58,280 --> 00:27:59,480
Qiuhua,

476
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:05,760
and Chuyi.

477
00:28:07,200 --> 00:28:08,680
I killed them all.

478
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:21,920
Am I right?

479
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:23,200
Wang Mang.

480
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:31,040
Have you lived up to Qiuhua's request?

481
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:42,240
Be good, Zhen'er.

482
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,400
Your mother is gone.

483
00:28:49,760 --> 00:28:52,320
Uncle is leaving today, too.

484
00:28:55,040 --> 00:28:56,560
Take good care of yourself.

